That's what IAEA safeguards are for. They are quite effective (if you 
don't take into account the cases of India and Pakistan). Theoretically 
every ounce of fissile material has to be accounted for, and to be 
verified by inspections from Wien.

To get more info on that, you can yahoo! for 'Non-Proliferation Treaty' 
or go to www.iaea.org

